title: Reduce the CAKE emission rate for the farm and lottery by 50%.
body:
As a response to multiple community proposals around reducing daily emissions, we’re proposing to cut the block emissions from all farms and the lottery from 30 CAKE per block to 15 CAKE per block. Note that the 10 CAKE per block allocation for SYRUP will remain untouched.

This effectively means that all farms and the lottery will receive half as many rewards and leave us with a 25 CAKE block emission as opposed to 40 CAKE per block.

If passed, the above would also mean the lottery would only have one incentive injection per day instead of two.

We’re extremely appreciative of our early PancakeSwap community up until now - you are amazing early adopters! By joining our protocol early, you’ve been able to farm at a faster speed to help bootstrap our initial protocol. With this proposed emissions reduction, CAKE/SYRUP will no longer be as easy to attain.
author: 0x6eaf1b33b8672c5dc40aB8f4bA3A0111723126c7
